# Core stack

This repo is **Next.js** (App Router) + PostgreSQL + Prisma — not Laravel.

- Read `AGENTS.md` for Next.js agent rules before changing framework APIs.
- Broader platform standards (tenancy, security): user rules `00-project`, `20-security`, `50-multitenancy`.
- UI work: `.cursor/rules/frontend.mdc` when editing `**/*.tsx`.

Definition of done for UI changes: four states (loading, empty, error, success), design tokens from `app/globals.css`, `npm run build` passes.
